                           buff-coloured, sized and polished <material>paper</material> probably
                           handmade in the <placeName cert="high">Britain</placeName> with ~10 laid
                           lines per cm and 26 mm between chain lines.</support>
                        <extent>
                           <measure unit="folio" quantity="517">517 folios, 6 flyleaves (ff. iii +
                              517 + iii)</measure>. <dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
                              <height>268</height>
                              <width>155</width>
                           </dimensions>
